Package: LandUsePLN
Title: Access Land Use Data in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(c("Tinashe", "Michael"), "Tapera", , "ttapera@hsph.harvard.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Christina", "Draeger", , "christina.draeger@posteo.de", role = "com"),
    person("Christopher", "Golden", , "golden@hsph.harvard.edu", role = "cph")
  )
Description: This pipeline provides access to land use data endpoints. It
    is designed to be flexible and adaptable to various data sources and
    formats, allowing users to easily retrieve and analyze land use data
    for their specific needs.  The current pipeline retrieves land use
    data from the [ESA World Cover](https://esa-worldcover.org/en)
    dataset.
